TEMPLATES


- we can render PROPERTY and METHODS on a template dynamically using 

  syntax: {{ property_name/method_name }}
- we can break template into multiple line using backtick('') synbol to make it more readable.
  eg: template: `<h2> {{ property_name }} <h2> // rendering property
                 <p> {{ method_name }} <p>     // rendering method
                 `
- see courses.components.ts file for example.